accessibility.text: FittedBox, Align, etc can be used to resize and position widgets
MediaQuery size can be used to determine and set global breakpoints
LayoutBuilder can be used to display widgets based on available space allocated by parent
Be mindful when using global size properties in nested widgets
Before reaching for Stacks and Positioned, consider whether your layout can be achieved using one of the previously mentioned widgets
FittedBox, Align, etc can be used to resize and position widgets
MediaQuery size can be used to determine and set global breakpoints
LayoutBuilder can be used to display widgets based on available space allocated by parent
